# Story Readiness Checklist — <story id>
<!-- Generated to docs/checklists/story-readiness-<id>.md (or one shared file). Check per story before build. -->

- [ ] The story states a clear Goal.
- [ ] Context is self-contained — a cold builder needs nothing else.
- [ ] `Covers:` lists the requirement IDs (FR-/AC-) this story satisfies.
- [ ] Acceptance criteria are testable checkboxes.
- [ ] Out-of-scope is explicit.
- [ ] A concrete Verification command is given.
- [ ] `depends-on` IDs are valid and (before build) already merged.
- [ ] `[P]` and `Touches` are present; `[P]` stories have non-overlapping Touches.
- [ ] `Risk` is set and `Review lenses` are listed (`code-integrity-reviewer` plus any warranted).
- [ ] `Security-sensitive` / `Architecture-sensitive` flags match the story's actual scope.
